canonical:
  title: 韓信
  author: 李瓊仝
  language: lzh
  text: 少年胯下任譏訶晩歲還羞噲伍何豈是封侯無一飯平生涯分已踰多
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 韓信
  author: 李瓊仝
  language: lzh
  text: 少年胯下任譏訶。晩歲還羞噲伍何。豈是封侯無一飯。平生涯分已踰多。
korean:
  title: 한신
  author: 이경동
  language: kor
  text: |-
    소년 쩍엔 다리 밑에서 마음대로 조롱하게 하고
    늘그막에는 도리어 번쾌와 짝되는 것 부끄러워 하였다
    어찌하여 후에 봉하였어도 밥 한 그릇 없었던가
    한평생의 분수가 이미 너무 많았더라
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_1450_020_0780&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 번쾌(樊噲) : '
    value: 예전에 한신의 부하였었다. 그러던 것이 한나라가 통일된 뒤에 한신을 앙으로 봉하였다가 뒤에 그 왕의 지위를 박탈당하고 후(侯)로 봉하여서 옛날 부하에 있던 사람과 동렬에 있게 되었다.
english:
  title: Han Xin
  author: Lee Gyeong-dong
  language: eng
  text: |-
    In youth, he bore mockery beneath the legs of the powerful.
    In old age, he felt shame standing equal to former servants.
    Why, though crowned a lord, did he lack even a single bowl of rice?
    A lifetime's fortune had already exceeded what fate allowed.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: Han Xin was a celebrated general of the Han Dynasty. Though originally powerful and respected, after the unification of the Han he was made a marquis, only to later lose his position and be demoted to the same rank as those who had once served under him—a humiliation that would ultimately lead to his downfall.
